    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Tiny Terraces” 是一个<strong>闲置农场游戏</strong>，你可以看到家伙做不同的任务在农场周围，因为你在游戏之外的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当前演示版本包括：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >17 种可种植作物 (目前 56 种作物中的 15 种)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 栋楼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 个装饰品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三种类型的家伙，启动器，小麦，和木材。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鸭子</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>种植作物：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种植庄稼，看着他们通过浇水、除草和收割来管理花园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289470/extras/14199aa96a49869a8bdbdc1a5f0e475d.poster.avif?t=1741668281\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289470/extras/14199aa96a49869a8bdbdc1a5f0e475d.webm?t=1741668281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289470/extras/14199aa96a49869a8bdbdc1a5f0e475d.mp4?t=1741668281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创造一些男人：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用特定的农作物和齿轮来制造更多的人来帮助管理农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289470/extras/9fdce604d82c571afbed791243a15685.poster.avif?t=1741668281\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289470/extras/9fdce604d82c571afbed791243a15685.webm?t=1741668281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289470/extras/9fdce604d82c571afbed791243a15685.mp4?t=1741668281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装饰：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用农作物生产的钱来购买装饰品来装饰你的农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>请将我的游戏添加到您的愿望清单!</strong> :)</p>",
